snippet.title: Elon Musk EXPOSES Amber Heard In Court & Reveals PRIVATE TEXTS...
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Amber Heard celebrity news
The case of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard in terms of their dual defamation of character lawsuits against one another is anything but, basic, straight forward, or sane. Because these two are bent on going after one another for very different reasons, and as a result, it makes you wonder just how it’s going to turn out. But soon, things will get a fresh start of sorts as new witnesses and evidence might just change things as we head towards the official court case. And one of those wild cards might just be Elon Musk. We’ll break it down for you, be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have, everyone! A look at the situation with Amber Heard’s court case and how Elon Musk (in addition to Johnny Depp and James Franco) might just turn things on her...or maybe even help her win. Are you tired of everything that’s going on with this case? Do you feel that this is so beneath everyone that it’s going to be impossible to believe when it’s over?
